Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.54,0:00:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Friendship! Romance! Mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:05.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We try our best because we've made those promises!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:08.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The strange case Ran encountered at the convenience store...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.09,0:00:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An outstanding deduction to save her friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.38,0:00:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:15.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:49.14,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,THE CONVENIENCE STORE TRAP\N(PART TWO)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:11.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:26.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.43,0:02:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:31.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you think of something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.94,0:02:33.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seem to be deep in thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:35.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:37.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:39.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's just that this is the first time we've seen your face without glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:44.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:46.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:48.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, those glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:50.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They look really old.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.33,0:02:51.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is something that's very precious to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:03:00.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only trace left in this world of a very, very important person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:01.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I wear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A very important person?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:08.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe a remembrance of an ex-boyfriend or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aside from that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:13.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you all understood this case yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:14.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It stopped-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:23.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The delivery truck?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:24.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:25.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That store assistant said it before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:31.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember, on the days Aya is on closing duty...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She neatly arranges the boxes that arrive before leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:38.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, they did mention something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:40.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, how is that connected to the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:43.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is it connected...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:47.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got my hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:51.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:56.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We brought the goods you ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:03:57.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:04:01.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll leave them in the passageway in front of the bathroom as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:02.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:05.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are still customers waiting to use the bathroom, so it's not a good time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:08.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, we'll bring them around again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:11.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We still have deliveries to a few other places.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:12.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll drop by again after we hit those.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:18.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The items can't be left outside of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.34,0:04:23.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the goods are left there, the customers can't get out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:26.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, we'll be back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:27.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:28.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:34.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the days Aya's on closing duty, she arranges the boxes in the bathroom passageway...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:41.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:43.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That famous line by Holmes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:49.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi often recites it with an arrogant expression on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:52.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the impossible is something, and something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:55.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you have eliminated the impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you have eliminated the impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:03.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,whatever remains,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:04.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,however improbable,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,must be the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:13.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you have eliminated the impossible, whatever remains, however improbable...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:15.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Must be the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you have eliminated the impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:22.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,whatever remains, however improbable,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,must be the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:26.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that the line?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:28.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that Ran just got something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:32.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:34.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be giving me false hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:37.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:39.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I have it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:51.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:53.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's already past 9:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:55.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to call my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:57.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The store's also cleared out a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:04.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:05.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:09.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, isn't it about time you confessed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:11.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I really didn't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:15.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like I'll have to leave this to the police, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:16.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:21.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't mind sharing my deduction, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I'm wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:25.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or if it isn't completely accurate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be inviting even more trouble for Aya...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:34.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it were him in this situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:53.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Cannot display"...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:57.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:06:59.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:02.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:04.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shi-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:06.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shi- Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.67,0:07:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not a big deal, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:13.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something I'd like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:14.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:20.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:23.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that Shinichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:29.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My friend's in a pinch right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know her too, Shinichi - it's Aya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} from middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:35.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Nanakawa, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the convenience store where she's working part-time, the inventory keeps disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's only on the days Aya's on cleaning and closing duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The manager is suspecting her of taking it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He threatened to call the police if she didn't confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The security cameras didn't record anyone shoplifting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:08:01.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Items were still disappearing even while the manager was keeping watch out front after closing time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:02.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why the manager thinks Aya is the culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:06.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, what sort of items disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:10.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Game software, CDs, DVDs, beverages, bento boxes, sweets, and snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and, Aya said that, among the customers, three of them are suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:18.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What types of people are those three?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:22.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first one reads game magazines in the store right until closing time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looks like a university student...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And all that he buys are cup noodles and instant food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:35.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Second is someone who often lets people ahead of him in line - a timid but especially polite salaryman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:39.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What he buys are things like toothbrush sets, shavers, dry batteries, and towels.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The last one is a stubborn old lady that likes to bargain over bento boxes that have nearly expired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:47.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems she never buys anything from this store.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:49.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:54.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The common link between those three is that they all often borrow the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:59.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, one month ago, after Aya was scolded by the manager outside the bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:01.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The items stopped disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But last night, just one month later - again on Aya's day - they disappeared once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:07.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it isn't unreasonable to suspect Nanakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't make it sound as though, you're speaking of a stranger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:15.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, there should be something else, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:20.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something Nanakawa does while on cleaning duty that the other store assistants fail to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other assistants leave the boxes that arrive before closing in the bathroom passageway, and head home...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:33.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Aya always arranges them properly before closing the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:36.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, if the security cameras were still working at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We could prove Aya's innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:43.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, the manager only has it record during operating hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:44.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:46.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would the stolen bento boxes happen to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just the ones that have nearly expired?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:51.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:52.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit is likely not a very bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:58.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You know who the culprit is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:01.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit is most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also tried to reason it out on my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:10.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh, and listen, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:14.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:18.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:29.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is my deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I considered a lot of things, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:34.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's not a shoplifter, nor an actual thief, nor Aya...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if it's unbelievable, this is all there is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:39.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How is it? Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:46.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, didn't I ask you not to laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:48.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:50.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not laughing at your deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just that, even though you managed to deduce that much, I can only imagine your troubled face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:55.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just find it really funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you mean, my deduction's right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.07,0:11:01.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:05.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop keeping me in suspense and tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:11.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unlike a certain someone, I'm not a famous detective who's always brimming with confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:14.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even detectives are normal humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:16.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They aren't almighty gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a detective presenting his deductions...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:24.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are times when he feels uneasy about it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:29.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He worries if maybe he overlooked something, and whether there are any other possibilities that remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:34.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why, when one's deduction hits the bull's-eye, it's the greatest feeling in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:38.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was only wondering if I should rob you of that sense of achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:40.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:45.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your husband - he's always saying profound things, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:48.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you think your deduction's correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go try it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:51.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Try it out"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.29,0:11:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should be all right, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a simple method you can use to unmask the culprit in front of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:01.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unmask the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you were the culprit, Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:06.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What circumstances would make it most difficult for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I were the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:32.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:35.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to borrow the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:07.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:18.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everybody, hurry! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll be burned alive if you don't hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:21.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop this now, I tell you, or it'll affect my business!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:29.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:31.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly what were you intending to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:10.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:11.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected, it was you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:19.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The especially polite salaryman customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, this man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:23.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:26.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who stole from the store at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And gave Aya such a hard time-the culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:30.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This person!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I kept watch over the front of the store all last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I didn't see this person sneaking in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course you didn't see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:41.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because this person...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has been living in the ceiling of this store's bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:48.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It may be unbelievable, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:52.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:55.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, after Aya closed the store...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:59.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would come out of the bathroom ceiling and go into the store itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would then take the beverages and food needed to sustain himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:04.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:07.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is only on closing duty two, three days a week - if he did that every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:09.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he takes a certain amount at a time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll have enough to last him two or three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:17.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why did he steal the game software and CDs?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:20.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe, he secretly exits the store occasionally...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:22.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And sells them for haircuts and baths.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he didn't, his hair would grow long and he'd get more and more dirty with time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:31.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To the point he'd never be able to come down from the ceiling again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:38.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wait, is it really possible to come and go from the bathroom without an employee or customer noticing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.89,0:15:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he suddenly came out of the bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:42.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or went in and never came out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone would get suspicious immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:47.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For an excessively polite and cautious person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:52.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, if he let people take their turn in the bathroom before him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And kept going until he was last in line...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:56.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one would see him enter the bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it wouldn't matter if he never came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he can get into the bathroom just before it gets crowded...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:09.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And get back into the store during the more bustling times...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:12.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could mingle with the other customers and avoid suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he lives in the ceiling...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:17.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,e would know the times that the bathroom is at its busiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Given that the store would obvious y be busy when the bathroom is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not even the store assistants would remember who entered and left here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:30.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about the toothbrush set, shavers, dry batteries, and towels that he buys?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:31.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The batteries are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:36.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the flashlight he uses when searching for items in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The others are simply daily necessities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:43.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a mirror and soap in the bathroom already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:45.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:46.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just as that girl said...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:49.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of the panels in the ceiling has been dislodged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:54.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, he really was hiding in the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's full of garbage, Manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:01.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What exactly is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:07.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And why is it that it's only when Aya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s on closing duty that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:10.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because Aya is very conscientious with her work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:13.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the boxes of goods placed in the passageway here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:19.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of the other assistants leave them lying around, which prevented him from getting through, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aya arranges them neatly on both sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:26.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how the culprit could come out of the bathroom in the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:31.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Ran, he only has to shift the boxes in order to get through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:36.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought that part was hard to justify as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:37.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:41.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While it's true he could just shift the boxes to get through...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the store assistants noticed the boxes had been moved...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They would begin to suspect someone had come through the passageway...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:50.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And turn their suspicions on the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:53.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy was just afraid they'd discover his hiding place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:56.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Due to this psychological effect, he didn't pass through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:17:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:01.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:04.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I still don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:08.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you stop stealing for an entire month?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:12.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you may have relied on selling those games and CDs to get by, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,f you hadn't stopped at that time, my suspicion of Aya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} would've grown even deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.18,0:18:23.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:25.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This man isn't really a bad person!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He likely heard from the ceiling that Aya was being scolded due to his actions...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:32.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And decided to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:35.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see - so that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:38.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He decided to steal the bento boxes that were about to expire...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:41.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to minimize losses to the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:42.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A thief is a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To have put Aya through all this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:51.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Causing Aya so much anguish...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:55.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... I will never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:19:00.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My most sincere apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:04.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was laid off by my last employer three months ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:06.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And chased out of my apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Starving, I staggered into this store...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:11.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I didn't have enough money to buy anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:14.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I was spacing out in the bathroom, the lights suddenly cut out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.52,0:19:18.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tried to get out, but couldn't since the door was locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:22.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, just as my eyes adjusted to the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:25.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw this mountain of food!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:27.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so, you stole from my store.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:28.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought that, with this much, a little wouldn't matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:32.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how much we have to sell in order to earn all of that back!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:43.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, you'll be paying back every bit of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:47.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But even if I wanted to, I don't have any at all to give you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:50.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll have you work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:53.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, of course, you won't get any pay at the onset.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're hiring me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:58.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even after all of this trouble I've given you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:04.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I started this store from scratch as well, so it's not that I don't understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.45,0:20:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:09.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.75,0:20:11.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just be sure to work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:12.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, sorry to spoil the moment, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:19.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you please give a proper apology to Aya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:20.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:28.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:30.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's great, Aya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:35.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:41.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Ran, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just have to leave it to Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.82,0:20:49.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lady Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Shinichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.45,0:20:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.16,0:20:56.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not a big deal, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:58.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you been to my house recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:01.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:05.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:07.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:10.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't Ran, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.90,0:22:44.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how it is - I'll be staying over at Sensei's house tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.53,0:22:48.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have dinner downstairs at Poirot, all right, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.03,0:22:48.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.11,0:22:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.36,0:22:54.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was supposed to be Sensei's farewell party...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.41,0:22:56.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she's drunk and asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.00,0:23:01.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's probably at ease now, since she gets to finally return home after so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:03.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.04,0:23:05.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.80,0:23:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.47,0:23:11.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was saved by him once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.68,0:23:13.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's mortifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.48,0:23:19.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.56,0:23:25.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A photograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.04,0:23:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.50,0:23:42.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
